//
//   CreateVolume (CSI)
//     ├─ StageVolume(RPC)  — backend: create zvol / LV / …
//     └─ MountVolume(RPC)  — protocol target: export over NVMe-oF / iSCSI / NFS
//
//   ControllerPublishVolume (CSI)
//     └─ AllowInitiator(RPC) — add initiator NQN/IQN/IP to ACL
//
//   ControllerUnpublishVolume (CSI)
//     └─ DenyInitiator(RPC)  — remove initiator from ACL
//
//   DeleteVolume (CSI)
//     ├─ UnmountVolume(RPC) — unexport: tear down protocol target entry
//     └─ DeleteVolume(RPC)  — backend: destroy zvol / LV / …
//
//   Cross-node migration / backup (out-of-band, not part of CSI spec)
//     ├─ ExportVolume(RPC)  — server-stream: zfs send / dd out of volume
//     └─ ImportVolume(RPC)  — client-stream: zfs receive / dd into volume

